config TEST_CALL_CHAIN
	bool "Test Call Chain Application"
	default n
	depends on OSAL && HAL && PDL && PCONFIG && ACONFIG
	help
	  Complete call chain test application.

	  This application tests the complete call chain from APP layer
	  through ACONFIG, PDL, PCONFIG to HAL layer.

	  Test functions:
	    - TestCallChain_MCU_CAN() - Test a TC mapping resolved through MCU path
	    - TestCallChain_MCU_Serial() - Test a second MCU-backed TC mapping
	    - TestCallChain_PowerControl() - Test power-control TC mapping
	    - TestCallChain_RunAll() - Run all tests

	  This is a debug/verification tool and should not be included
	  in production builds.
